gantt
    title Sprint 1 Task Execution Plan by Parent User Story
    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat  %d %b
    excludes weekends

    %% For tasks with multiple prerequisites, the bar is anchored to the latest dependency.
    %% The task label notes the broader dependency context where helpful.

    section PBI-031 - Register member organization
    PBI-039 Define org schema, uniqueness, status model            :crit, pbi039, 2026-03-16, 2d
    PBI-040 Implement org creation API and validation              :crit, pbi040, after pbi039, 3d
    PBI-041 Implement admin registration UI and feedback           :pbi041, after pbi039, 2d
    PBI-042 Add authorization, audit logging, data handling        :pbi042, after pbi040, 2d
    PBI-043 E2E validation, regression, docs, demo evidence       :pbi043, after pbi042, 2d

    section PBI-032 - Define and maintain platform roles
